The old DynamicTaskList would word-wrap the text of a task entry if it was too wide for the browser window. But not any more. This limits the usability of the DynamicTaskList: sometimes I want to put more than just a couple of words there.

The ability to supplement that "Headline" with some "body text" would be even nicer - I imagine the "body text" would only appear if you use the button to expand an entry.

