We recently had the need to treat a Page as a "drop box".  Here, drop box is defined as a page where anyone can attach files or create children pages, but could NOT see what anyone else has attached or added.

Current Page Restrictions are not fine grained enough to allow this Write/Create but not Read permission configuration.

We use our confluence for a lot of internal file tracking tasks.  These files are often confidential to the larger user base.  The ability to upload a document which no one can see but the Page Admin would help tremendously.  We're really trying to move away from using Email to move these documents around.

