The 'Page Deleted' page should have a 'Browse Space' link somewhere on it. At the moment a deleted page is effectively a dead end, with breadcrumb navigation being the only access to other content in that space.

In the scenario where the 'Home' page for a space is deleted, the breadcrumb navigation is also rendered useless since clicking on the space name simply takes you to the same page - the Dashboard becomes the only method by which to view content.
